{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 44,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الدُّخَانِ",
    "englishName": "Ad-Dukhaan",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Smoke",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 59,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4415,
        "text": "Ha Mim.",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4416,
        "text": "By the Book that makes things clear,",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4417,
        "text": "surely We sent it down on a blessed night, We have always sent warnings,",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4418,
        "text": "on that night every wise decree is specified",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4419,
        "text": "by Our own command -- We have been sending messages,",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4420,
        "text": "as a mercy from your Lord, He hears all and knows all,",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4421,
        "text": "He is the Lord of heaven and earth and all that is between them, if only you would really believe,",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4422,
        "text": "there is no deity save Him: It is He who gives both life and death -- He is your Lord, and the Lord of your forefathers,",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4423,
        "text": "yet, they toy with their doubts.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4424,
        "text": "Wait, then, for the Day when the sky brings forth plainly visible clouds of smoke.",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4425,
        "text": "That will envelop the people. This will be a painful punishment.",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4426,
        "text": "Then they will say, \"Lord, relieve us from this torment, for truly we are now believers in You.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4427,
        "text": "How can they benefit from admonition, seeing that a messenger had already come to them explaining things clearly?",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4428,
        "text": "Then they turned away from him and said, \"He is a madman, taught by others!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4429,
        "text": "Were We to ease the torment for a while, you would still revert to denial of the truth.",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4430,
        "text": "On the Day We inflict the direst scourge upon all sinners, We will certainly exact retribution.",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4431,
        "text": "We tried the people of Pharaoh before them: a noble messenger was sent to them,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4432,
        "text": "saying, \"Hand over God's servants to me. I am a trustworthy messenger for you.",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4433,
        "text": "Do not set yourselves above God: I bring you clear authority.",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4434,
        "text": "I have sought refuge with my Lord and your Lord lest you stone me [to death].",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4435,
        "text": "If you do not believe in me, at least keep away from me.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4436,
        "text": "Then he cried out to his Lord, \"These are sinful people.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4437,
        "text": "God said, \"Set out with My servants by night, for you will certainly be pursued.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4438,
        "text": "Leave the sea behind you parted; they are a host destined to be drowned.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4439,
        "text": "How many gardens and fountains they left behind them,",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4440,
        "text": "and cornfields and splendid buildings,",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4441,
        "text": "and pleasant things in which they delighted!",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4442,
        "text": "Such was their end, and what had been theirs We gave to other people to inherit.",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4443,
        "text": "Neither heaven nor earth wept for them, nor were they allowed any respite.",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4444,
        "text": "We saved the Children of Israel from their humiliating torment",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4445,
        "text": "at the hands of Pharaoh: he was a tyrant who exceeded all bounds.",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4446,
        "text": "We knowingly chose them above all other people",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4447,
        "text": "and showed them signs in which there was a clear test.",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4448,
        "text": "Yet those who deny the truth say,",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4449,
        "text": "there is nothing beyond our first death; we shall not be raised again.",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4450,
        "text": "So bring our fathers [back], if what you say is true.",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4451,
        "text": "Are they better than the people of Tubba' and those who came before them? We destroyed them, because they were guilty of sin.",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4452,
        "text": "We did not idly create the heavens and the earth and all that lies between them;",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4453,
        "text": "We did not create them save with a purpose, yet most people have no knowledge of this.",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4454,
        "text": "Truly, the Day of Decision is the appointed time for all of them,",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4455,
        "text": "the Day when no friend shall be of the least avail to another, nor shall any be helped,",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4456,
        "text": "save those to whom God shows mercy. Surely, He is the Mighty, the Merciful One.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4457,
        "text": "Surely the fruit of the Zaqqum tree",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4458,
        "text": "shall be food for the sinners:",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4459,
        "text": "like the dregs of oil, it shall boil in their bellies,",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4460,
        "text": "like the boiling of hot water.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4461,
        "text": "[A voice will cry], \"Seize him and drag him into the midst of Hell.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4462,
        "text": "Then pour boiling water over his head as punishment.",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4463,
        "text": "Taste this; you who considered yourself the mighty, the honourable!",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4464,
        "text": "This is what you doubted?\"",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4465,
        "text": "But those mindful of God will be in a safe place,",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4466,
        "text": "among gardens and springs,",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4467,
        "text": "dressed in fine silk and in rich brocade, and they will face each other:",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4468,
        "text": "so it will be. We shall wed them to maidens with large, dark eyes.",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4469,
        "text": "They will call therein for every kind of fruit, in peace and security.",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4470,
        "text": "They will not taste death therein, save the first death. God will save them from the torment of Hell",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4471,
        "text": "as an act of grace. That will be the supreme triumph.",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4472,
        "text": "We have made this Quran easy to understand, in your own language, so that they may take heed.",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4473,
        "text": "Wait then; they too are waiting.",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "en.wahiduddin",
      "language": "en",
      "name": "Wahiduddin Khan",
      "englishName": "Wahiduddin Khan",
      "format": "text",
      "type": "translation",
      "direction": "ltr"
    }
  }
}